GridUseCaseScenario.Name: SCADA for Observability
GridUseCaseScenario.Overview: SCADA for Observability allows the utility to not only have visibility into its distribution assets, but also have assets which provide a rich enough data set to gain insight from their data.

ApplicationScenario.Name: Feeder Line Device Sensor Data Acquisition
ApplicationScenario.Narrative: SCADA sends a command to the Feeder Line Device in order to retrieve sensor data. This can be used to determine physical conditions of the unit.
